Test Title: Verify export button opens export options
Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Instructions  > List Instructions
2-Click on export button
Description: Ensure that clicking on the Extract button displays export format options (PDF, XLS).
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page

Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Instructions  > List Instructions
2-Click on export button
3-Choose PDF
Description: Check that the system generates a PDF file containing the same data displayed in the instruction list.
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page
Expected Result: A PDF file should be downloaded showing the same data as the instruction list.
Actual Result: PDF file downloaded successfully and showed the same data in the instruction list
Comments: PDF generated successfully, and data matched

Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Instructions  > List Instructions
2-Click on export button
3-Choose XLS
Description: Check that the system generates a XLS file containing the same data displayed in the instruction list.
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page
Expected Result: A XLS file should be downloaded showing the same data as the instruction list.
Actual Result: XLS file downloaded successfully and showed the same data in the instruction list
Comments: XLS generated successfully, and data matched

Test Title: Verify that clicking the Search button performs the correct search action
Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Instructions  > List Instructions
2-Type keyword in the search field
3-Click on Search button
Description: Validate that entering a keyword filters the instruction list and shows only matching records
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page
Expected Result: Only instructions containing the search keyword should be displayed in the list
Actual Result:
The search results appear correctly while typing in the search field (live search works).
However, once the Search button is clicked, the system redirects to another unrelated page instead of showing filtered results
Comments: Search button in not working correctly

Test Title: Verify that the selected record are permanently removed after confirming deletion
Steps:
1-Go to System Settings > Instructions  > List Instructions
2-Click on the delete icon
3-Click yes in the confirmation pop-up
Description: Ensure that deleting record works correctly
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page
Expected Result: The deleted record should be removed from the list
Actual Result: System deletes the selected record from the list

Test Title: Verify cancel button in delet confirmation works correctly
Steps:

2-Click on delete icon
3-Click on cancel button
Description: Ensure that cancelling deletion works correctly
Preconditions:
1-User logged in
2-user in List Instructions page
